@user4 @user3 You can do it! And I'm happy to help you with my experiences.
Website: Check out @user5. It seems simple, looks good, and is open source. I'll switch one of my websites to it before the next renewal.
Signal: Check out cal.com. It's an open-source calendar service with integrations that allow you to schedule video calls using Element Call, Jitsi, etc. Signal is also supported, but I haven't yet tried whether it's for messages or video.
I can recommend @user6. E2EE, decentralized, Open Source.
